Practical Customer 360 / RFM Examples
------------------------------------------------------------------
Recency Status :
-------------------------------------------------
RecencyStatus = 
IF(Customer[Recency]<=30,"Active",
   IF(Customer[Recency]<=90,"At Risk","Churn"))


Monetary Default :
------------------------------------------------
TotalSpent = COALESCE(SUM(Sales[Amount]),0)


Loyalty Category using SWITCH :
-------------------------------------------------
LoyaltySegment = SWITCH(TRUE(),
   Customer[Frequency]>=20 && Customer[Monetary]>=5000,"Champion",
   Customer[Frequency]>=10 && Customer[Monetary]>=2000,"Loyal",
   Customer[Recency]>90,"At Risk",
   "Others")
